snippet.title: Jedi Knight: Jedi Academy - Launch Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
The online multiplayer classic returns with modernized controls! Take on the role of a new student eager to learn the ways of the Force from Jedi Master Luke Skywalker. 

Star Wars Jedi Knight: Jedi Academy releases on Nintendo Switch today!

https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/star-wars-jedi-knight-jedi-academy-switch/
